    "Consider a dataset of n examples, D = {(x k, y k)} k=1,...,n, where",
    "is the vec- tor of features and y k ∈ R is the target value.",
    "The goal of the learning task is to train a function F: R m → R which minimises the expected loss EL(y, F(x)).",
    "A GB procedure iteratively builds a sequence of approximations F t: R m → R, t = 0, 1,.",
    "using a so-called greedy stagewise approach 39."
